    {
      "id": "PopularPost351896",
      "post_content": "**Super bad combo:**  \n[Hive Mind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hive Mind)  \n[Sigarda. Host of Herons](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sigarda. Host of Herons)  \n[Epicenter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Epicenter)  \n[Naturalize](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Naturalize)  \n[Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell)  \n  \n1. Have Hive Mind and Sigarda out  \n2. Cast Epicenter, have it copied by opponent  \n3. Naturalize the Hive Mind  \n4. Counter your own Epicenter, choose not to pay  \n5. Opponent now controls the effect, so because of Sigarda it can't cause you to sacrifice permanents.  \n  \n\\* NB: Requires Threshold for opponent. [Mind Sculpt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Sculpt) them if necessary.  \n\\* NB: Can be done without Naturalize/Counterspell combo if you don't have Threshold and they do.",
      "posted_by": "Alchemix",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost351896\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\"><b>Super bad combo:</b><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hive Mind\">Hive Mind</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sigarda. Host of Herons\">Sigarda. Host of Herons</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Epicenter\">Epicenter</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Naturalize\">Naturalize</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell\">Counterspell</a><br/><br/>1. Have Hive Mind and Sigarda out<br/>2. Cast Epicenter, have it copied by opponent<br/>3. Naturalize the Hive Mind<br/>4. Counter your own Epicenter, choose not to pay<br/>5. Opponent now controls the effect, so because of Sigarda it can't cause you to sacrifice permanents.<br/><br/>* NB: Requires Threshold for opponent. <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Sculpt\">Mind Sculpt</a> them if necessary.<br/>* NB: Can be done without Naturalize/Counterspell combo if you don't have Threshold and they do.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy103107\">Alchemix</span>\r\n                                (11/19/2013 12:51:22 AM)\r\n    